---
const title = "Shark Valley Plex";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>FAQ — Shark Valley Plex</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background-color: #111827;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      background-color: #1f2937;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #374151;
      padding: 0 24px;
      height: 64px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .nav-inner {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .nav-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      background: #374151;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .nav-links a.active {
      color: #fff;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #6366f1;
    }

    .btn-request {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7);
      color: #fff !important;
      padding: 7px 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    /* PAGE */
    .page {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 48px 24px 64px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #f9fafb;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* FAQ ITEMS */
    .faq-item {
      background: #1f2937;
      border: 1px solid #374151;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .faq-item:hover { border-color: #4b5563; }

    .faq-item h4 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #f3f4f6;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .faq-item p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .faq-item a {
      color: #6366f1;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      background: #1f2937;
      border-top: 1px solid #374151;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    /* MOBILE */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      nav { padding: 0 16px; height: 56px; }
      .nav-links { gap: 2px; }
      .nav-links a { font-size: 12px; padding: 6px 8px; }
      .btn-request { padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 13px; }
      .page { padding: 32px 16px 48px; }
      h1 { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a class="nav-logo" href="/">
        <img src="/images/os_logo_filled.png" alt="Shark Valley Plex" height="40" />
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/faq" class="active">FAQ</a>
        <a href="https://stats.uptimerobot.com/9vb3fSvvMq" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Status</a>
        <a class="btn-request" href="https://request.sharkvalleyplex.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Request</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="page">

    <img src="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg" alt="FAQ" style="width:100%; max-width:720px; height:auto; border-radius:12px; display:block; margin:0 auto 40px;" />

    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>What is Plex?</h4>
      <p>Plex is a free service that allows you to share your media. By subscribing to a membership, you are given access to my server, which includes thousands of Movies and TV Shows.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Where is Plex available?</h4>
      <p>Plex is available in almost every country in the world. As long as you have internet access and a smart device, you will be able to access the server.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Where can I watch Plex?</h4>
      <p>You can watch Plex instantly online from your personal computer or any internet-connected device that offers the Plex app. This includes Amazon Fire TV, Android TV, Apple TV, Chromecast, Roku, smart TVs (LG, Hisense, Samsung, VIZIO), smartphones, tablets, game consoles, and more.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>How much does it cost?</h4>
      <p>Memberships are currently priced at $10 per month.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>How do I subscribe?</h4>
      <p>Just click the <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/eVq8wP16Fe3t8NWaGofjG01">Subscribe</a> button on the home page. Once we receive confirmation, we will provide an account.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Do I need an account?</h4>
      <p>No, please do not make a Plex account. We will provide one for you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>What if something I want to watch is not available?</h4>
      <p>You can request any Movie or TV Show, and we will add it to our platform, usually within 24 hours.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>How many streams can I watch at once?</h4>
      <p>Accounts are limited to 3 continuous streams.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Are there any restrictions or rules?</h4>
      <p>Please do not share your account with anyone outside of your household. If your friends are interested in the service, refer them here.</p>
    </div>

  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 Shark Valley Plex. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
